Title: Designates a portion of the state highway system in the village of Unionville as the "Appalachian Trailway Highway"
Summary: Designates a portion of state highway 284 in the village of Unionville as the "Appalachian Trailway Highway".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system in the village of Unionville as the "Appalachian Trailway Highway"
